'''分离龙族'''（学名：Kritosaurini）是[[鸭嘴龙科|鸭嘴龙科]][[栉龙亚科|栉龙亚科]][[恐龙|恐龙]]的一个[[演化支|演化支]]，生存于[[白垩纪|白垩纪]]晚期。

==发现与命名==
该分类群第一个被发现的成员是[[分离龙|分离龙]]，由[[古生物学家|古生物学家]][[巴纳姆·布朗|巴纳姆·布朗]]命名于1910年。<ref name=BB10>{{cite journal |last=Brown |first=Barnum |authorlink=Barnum Brown |year=1910 |title=The Cretaceous Ojo Alamo beds of New Mexico with description of the new dinosaur genus ''Kritosaurus'' |journal=Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History |volume=28 |issue=24 |pages=267–274 |url=http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/handle/2246/1398 |access-date=2017-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006075551/http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/dspace/handle/2246/1398 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |url-status=live }}</ref>四年后，[[加拿大|加拿大]]古生物学家[[劳伦斯·赖博|劳伦斯·赖博]]命名了[[钩鼻龙|钩鼻龙]]。<ref name=LL14>{{cite journal |last=Lambe |first=Lawrence M. |authorlink=Lawrence Lambe |year=1914 |title=On ''Gryposaurus notabilis'', a new genus and species of trachodont dinosaur from the Belly River Formation of Alberta, with a description of the skull of ''Chasmosaurus belli'' |journal=The Ottawa Naturalist |volume=27 |issue=11 |pages=145–155 }}</ref>随后，人们立即意识到这两个分类群之间的相似性，在整个二十世纪，后一个属的有效性受到怀疑，有人认为二者是同一物种。<ref name=BB14>{{cite journal |last=Brown |first=Barnum |authorlink=Barnum Brown |year=1914 |title=Cretaceous Eocene correlation in New Mexico, Wyoming, Montana, Alberta |journal=Geological Society of America Bulletin |volume=25 |doi=10.1130/gsab-25-355 |pages=355–380 |url=https://zenodo.org/record/1448379/files/article.pdf |access-date=2020-11-14 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116013343/https://zenodo.org/record/1448379/files/article.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CWG16>{{cite journal |last=Gilmore |first=Charles W. |authorlink=Charles Whitney Gilmore |year=1916 |title=Contributions to the geology and paleontology of San Juan County, New Mexico. 2. Vertebrate faunas of the Ojo Alamo, Kirtland and Fruitland Formations |journal=United States Geological Survey Professional Paper |volume=98-Q |pages=279–302 }}</ref>直到20世纪90年代，它们才被确认为不同的属。<ref name=WH90>{{cite book |last=Weishampel |first=David B. |authorlink=David B. Weishampel |author2=Horner, Jack R. |editor= Weishampel, David B. |editor2=Dodson, Peter |editor3=Osmólska Halszka|title=The Dinosauria |url=https://archive.org/details/dinosauria0000unse_k1f9 |edition=1st |year=1990 |publisher=University of California Press |location=Berkeley |isbn=978-0-520-06727-1 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosauria0000unse_k1f9/page/534 534]–561 |chapter=Hadrosauridae}}</ref>大约在这个时候，与之相关的鸭嘴龙类如[[纳秀毕吐龙|纳秀毕吐龙]]<ref name=HL93>{{cite book |last=Hunt |first=Adrian P. |author2=Lucas, Spencer G. |year=1993 |chapter=Cretaceous vertebrates of New Mexico |editor=Lucas, S.G. |editor2=Zidek, J. |title=Dinosaurs of New Mexico |series=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin, '''2''' |publisher=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science |location=Albuquerque, New Mexico |pages=77–91}}</ref>和[[独孤龙|独孤龙]]<ref name="MBS79">{{cite journal | title=Phylogeny and palaeobiogeography of hadrosaurian dinosaurs | author=Brett-Surman, M. K. | journal=Nature | year=1979 | volume=277 | issue=5697 | pages=560–562}}</ref>被发现，对该分类群的现代解释开始发展。<ref name=MBS89/>

该分类群由{{link-en|迈克尔·布雷特·苏尔曼|Michael Brett-Surman}}于1989年首次作为一个[[族_(生物)|族]]提出。<ref name=MBS89>{{cite journal | title=A revision of the Hadrosauridae (Reptilia: Ornithischia) and their evolution during the Campanian and Maastrichtian. | author=Brett-Surman, Michael Keith. | journal=Faculty of the Graduate School of Arts and Sciences of the George Washington University | year=1989}}</ref>2014年{{link-en|阿尔伯特·普里托·马尔克斯|Albert Prieto-Márquez}}首次将其定义为“鸭嘴龙中最为独有的一个分支，包括：纳瓦霍[[分离龙|分离龙]]（Brown，1910年）、著名[[钩鼻龙|钩鼻龙]]（Lambe，1914年）和奥氏[[纳秀毕吐龙|纳秀毕吐龙]]（Hunt与Lucas，1993年）”。<ref name="APM14">{{cite journal | title=Skeletal morphology of Kritosaurus navajovius (Dinosauria: Hadrosauridae) from the Late Cretaceous of the North American south-west, with an evaluation of the phylogenetic systematics and biogeography of Kritosaurini. | author=Prieto-Márquez, A. | journal=Journal of Systematic Palaeontology | year=2014 | volume=12 | issue=2 | pages=133–175 | doi=10.1080/14772019.2013.770417}}</ref>

